Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜要去留学？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.04,0:00:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 毕业以后就到美国...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我想更早一点说出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.89,0:00:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐明明才刚出院
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往前迈进一步了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...难得你出院 回到大家身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要离别
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 爸爸妈妈都很明白茜的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.84,0:00:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.59,0:00:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.14,0:01:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜朝着自己的梦想 一路走了过来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使发生了再痛苦的事情 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.64,0:01:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也终于迈出为了圆梦的重要一步 要向前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.65,0:01:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.90,0:01:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在已经很健康了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心我了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.79,0:01:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.29,0:01:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜就不用担心 去追逐自己的梦想就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.93,0:01:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 加油哦 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.86,0:01:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
